The Telegraph - Calcutta : Nation

 Tease suicide

 Madurai, April 14 (PTI): A man has been arrested for teasing a 16-year-old by pulling her dupatta, which drove her to suicide, police said.

 The girl had gone to attend a temple festival in Sivaganga district when the youth asked her to marry him. On being rebuked, he pulled her dupatta. Unable to bear the shame, the girl set herself on fire. She died yesterday. 




